{"type": "article", "id": 27513, "title": "Gucci 推出 DIY 服务，以及，Kate Moss衬衫来一件么？｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-05-30T10:34:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5264, "name": "童装"}, {"id": 1241, "name": "男装"}, {"id": 14026, "name": "度假系列"}, {"id": 15755, "name": "走秀"}, {"id": 28297, "name": "DIY定制服务"}, {"id": 28298, "name": "90 年代"}, {"id": 35, "name": "复古"}, {"id": 3677, "name": "衬衫"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 28299, "name": "Shiseido"}, {"id": 8914, "name": "Mr Porter"}, {"id": 28300, "name": "Maison Kitsuné"}, {"id": 2601, "name": "宝马"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 28301, "name": "Mitchell & Ness"}, {"id": 129, "name": "Kate Moss"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120439elTiq5FrpCzHyZIS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Gucci-launches-do-it-yourself-service,697600.html#.V0slS4QrJQY\"><b>Gucci 推出 DIY 服务</b></a>｜Gucci 近日推出一项新的 DIY 服务，允许顾客个性化定制产品，灵感来自创意总监 Alessandro Michele。新项目 5 月 25 日率先在 Gucci 米兰旗舰店开始，之后将推广至世界各地门店。可选定制内容包含一系列酒神包，添加不同刺绣、金属等饰物，首字母缩写等等。随后将逐渐扩展到 Ace 球鞋和 Princetown 鞋，也包括一部分的男女装。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/mergers-acquisitions/adidas-sells-us-sports-clothing-business-mitchell-ness-10438864/\"><b>adidas 出售旗下美式运动品牌 Mitchell &amp; Ness</b></a>｜adidas 近日宣布已与私募资本集团 Juggernaut Capital Partners 旗下一公司达成最终协议，出售旗下美式运动品牌 Mitchell &amp; Ness。将更加关注核心业务，adidas 表示这一品牌已不符合去年 11 月发布的新战略，后者将在未来五年内把重心放在女子、儿童、跑步、足球和运动经典五大系列上。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/louis-vuitton-rio-de-janeiro-michael-burke-nicolas-ghesquiere10439398-10439398/\"><b>LV 2017 度假系列大秀在里约举行</b></a>｜Louis Vuitton 2017 年度假系列大秀周六在巴西里约当代艺术博物馆（MAC）上演，这座城市的多彩、热带风情和运动、未来感十足的服装系列相混合。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021204269IJXGhmjYd0LSBQn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120426Pncohp6QkV7u95f3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120427FKxO67pHJdYzZBCI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120427cnHvomJDQpT9RSq5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120428f0UMuZSY4q2vWd9z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p>Amazon 旗下的 EASTDANE，即“男士版的 SHOPBOP” <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/y3-sport-adidas-yohji-yamamoto-east-dane\">拍摄了 Y-3 的春夏系列特辑</a>:</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120428KF8N6BSGRsqnmMz5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021204298VZNWXt5gDxqKCwR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120430j1XK9dHprR0kwYCe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Kate Moss 与很受欢迎的衬衫品牌 Equipment 合作推出了一个胶囊系列：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120430Xi4cuM5WzYI6Jhqe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54282536\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120430oQDeBpSaqyRZfFAG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56810244\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120431x5lYmp02nT1OziMy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51694915\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120431wdx2gGDZWH4oLjQe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56156502\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120432fS9MYonLhpIFzi1d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5088634\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"> Gucci 的每件单品都很光彩夺目，<a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/5/27/11715288/gucci-children-collection\">童装系列也不错</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120432i0CxaZBzAhMYSf4b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120433xSy9FQPNhkum4Y8v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120433bykmjuTHFESihONW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120434vjrKEQIqGtDpzFM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120434MExN7Rv59LeoS2KB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120434p9JhTIXQLgCocnZN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2016/5/maison-kitsune-mr-porter-capsule-collection\">Maison Kitsuné 与男装奢侈品电商 Mr Porter 合作推出一个胶囊系列</a>，灵感来自悠闲的旅行，包含 18 件单品。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120435Pvz1QbeSsfMxG0JK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.725\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120435cp8AluQ6wB20yvji.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120436hUxy8TDc6zKCsb0W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2016/5/puma-is-staying-cool-with-ice-cream-collection\">Puma 发布一个冰淇淋球鞋系列</a>，包括奶油色的香草、棕色的巧克力、米黄色的黄油核桃。5 月 28 日上市，每双 75 美元。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120436XL1cTG7qyiSEKD4H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66595745\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">宝马为庆祝 M3 车型诞生 30 周年，<b><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/bmw-30-years-m3\">推出 30 周年特别版 M3 车型</a>。</b>基于 M3 竞赛套件版的升级，配色为独特的澳门蓝金属车漆，采用 Merino 真皮运动座椅，搭载升级后的 3.0T 双涡轮增压六缸发动机。限量发布 500 台。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120437xW1Xj4kdEce9IHap.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120437u3NM4xU2nwBLrKec.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120438JYz54DdcpIqiK6LA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120438u5HsG2VU37xgmW9n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120439TtHobpcnldk3Ge79.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}